    "in the \"Obtain Diamond\" task.",
    "Typical reinforcement learning-based agents often struggle with the complexity of Minecraft due to the long time horizon of the task, which can lead to difficulties in learning and adapting.",
    "In contrast, Zhu et al. (2023) leverages LLMs to enable a hierarchical decomposition of complex tasks into manageable sub-goals and structured actions.",
    "This approach yields significantly higher efficiency and robustness, allowing agents to better navigate and interact with the Minecraft environment.",
    "GITM integrates the logical reasoning and knowledge base of LLMs with text-based knowledge and memory, enabling effective interaction with the environment and the pursuit of intricate, long-term objectives."
